snippet.title: (No EAS) Rosmen, NC/Dallas, TX - Texas AMBER Alert - 08/16/2021
snippet.description:
https://mesonet.agron.iastate.edu/wx/afos/p.php?pil=CAECRP&e=202108170405

BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
1105 PM CDT MON AUG 16 2021

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THE TRANSYLVANIA COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR CARLOS 
MANUEL CHINCHILLA-VAZQUEZ, HISPANIC MALE, 15 YEARS OLD, 5 FEET 7 
INCHES, 180 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND WEARING A WHITE 
T-SHIRT.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR A HISPANIC MALE, POSSIBLY IN THEIR 30'S, 
IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A DARK GRAY, 2020-2021, NISSAN ROGUE WITH
UNKNOWN LICENSE PLATES.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN ROSMAN, NC, BUT THEIR PHONE HAS
PINGED IN DALLAS.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER.

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE
TRANSYLVANIA COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE AT 8 2 8 8 8 4 3 1 6 8.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS TRANSYLVANIA COUNTY SHERIFF'S 
OFFICE AT 8 2 8 8 8 4 3 1 6 8.

$$
